name: Qdrant OpenMetrics endpoint health
description: Returns `CRITICAL` if the Agent is unable to connect to the Qdrant OpenMetrics endpoint, otherwise returns `OK`.

name: Qdrant readyz HTTP check
description: Returns `OK` if /readyz endpoint returns a 200 response, otherwise returns `CRITICAL`.

name: Qdrant livez HTTP check
description: Returns `OK` if /livez endpoint returns a 200 response, otherwise returns `CRITICAL`.
